title: Introducing the NutriBullet Pro - 900 Series
description:
We are thrilled to introduce a new member to the NutriBullet family.  The NutriBullet 900 boasts a more powerful motor with 25,000 RPMs, new accessories and a Blast with an even smoother finish.  You are going to love this product.  Check out our video to see all the latest updates!

For more information, please visit: https://www.nutriliving.com/

Follow us @theNutriBullet:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thenutribullet
Instagram: https://instagram.com/thenutribullet/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/thenutribullet
Vine: https://vine.co/The.NutriBullet
Pinterest: https://www.pinterest.com/thenutribullet/
transcripts: many people have been asking what's the difference between the nutribullet and the nutribullet 900 so it nutribullet were continually striving to bring you the best product out there and we can do that by engaging with millions of our customers on a daily basis we review their feedback and we listen to what you guys are saying and we've brought you the nutribullet 900 series its basically the nutribullet 2.0 here's our original nutribullet that we all know and love and this is our new 900 series I want to take some time to point out the differences between the two series the nutribullet 900 has 900 watts of power that's 25,000 rpms you'll be able to extract faster than ever before and you won't believe how smooth it is the nutribullet 900 comes with two extractor blades too-tall cups and for the first time ever we're debuting our 32 ounce colossal cup this is perfect for two blasters you will also get the flip top to go lid this is something that you guys have been asking about for the past year and I'm so excited to introduce it to you our leak proof design system allows you to throw it in a lunch bag or a gym bag and guess what no spilling and this life-changing recipes book it's full of recipes from nutria blasters just like you they share their favorite Blast recipes for energy diabetes hormone balance athletic performance along with all the success they've had with the nutribullet watch how fast this is even the toughest ingredients don't stand a chance in here I have kale blackberries raspberries and flaxseed and I'm going to top it off with some almond milk and watch this in just seconds now you have two blasts that blend perfectly every single time mmm delicious so there you have it the second generation nutribullet we hope you love it as much as we do
